reportColumnMetadata.name: Handled by IVR
reportColumnMetadata.description:
Handled by IVR
The total number of calls that have been handled by the IVR function.
Composed of: Connected, Not connected

reportColumnMetadata.name: Connected
reportColumnMetadata.description:
Connected
Number of calls that have been handled by the IVR function and been redirected to another number by the IVR function.
Included in: Handled by IVR - (Connected, Not connected)

reportColumnMetadata.name: Not connected
reportColumnMetadata.description:
Not connected
Number of calls that have been handled by the IVR function but not been redirected anywhere i.e. the call has been cancelled at the IVR function.
Included in: Handled by IVR - (Connected, Not connected)

reportColumnMetadata.name: (Avg) Call duration for IVR
reportColumnMetadata.description:
(Avg) Call duration for IVR
The average call duration of a call that has been handled by the IVR function.

reportColumnMetadata.name: Total call duration for IVR
reportColumnMetadata.description:
Total call duration for IVR
The total call duration for all calls that have been handled by the IVR function.

reportColumnMetadata.name: Terminated because of failure
reportColumnMetadata.description:
Terminated because of failure
Number of calls that have been terminated because of failure.

reportColumnMetadata.name: Transferred to
reportColumnMetadata.description:
Transferred to
Specification of where the function has transferred the calls to.

reportColumnMetadata.name: Group names
reportColumnMetadata.description: The names of the groups the object or group belong to

reportColumnMetadata.name: Object identifier
reportColumnMetadata.description: The unique identifier of the object the row represents

reportColumnMetadata.name: Type
reportColumnMetadata.description: Describes if the row represent the total, a group or a an object.

reportColumnMetadata.name: Depth in hierarchy
reportColumnMetadata.description: The level of the object/group is in the hierarchy. Indicates how many parent groups the object/group has.
